Socialfieds is a simple reusable Classifieds app for Django. The app is loosely modeled after Craigslist but with more of an emphasis on social networking.

Features:
Can be integrated with django-comments, django-messaging and django-profiles
Simple two field listing form that is easily expanded
Board, Category and Listing titles in url
Simple listing moderation

